<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="256" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1437,583,1977]" pageId="13" pageNumber="256">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,286,583,609]" pageId="13" pageNumber="256">Etymology.</emphasis>
This taxon is named after my good friend Jeffrey Gruber, who first collected it, in appreciation of his long-term support of my work and his generosity with sharing material.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
